title: Your timeline
subtitle: A suggested timeline of 10 working days is already entered below. This takes the process up to when the suppliers have submitted their responses, and allows a further 6 working days for you to decide what to do next and confirm that to the suppliers.
subtitle2: The clarification period is when the suppliers can ask you further questions before submitting their information. You must meet the deadline you set for responding to their questions.
subtitleDA: The dates and times form a suggested timeline for a simple procurement. You can amend them to suit your own requirements.
subtitleDA1: It's recommended that you set your times no later than 4pm on weekday. This is in case you need to contact CCS about your project.
